{% eIn workout settings, we want the ability to add a Gender. If the Gender is set (Male/Female/Both) then ONLY that gender will be able to receive that workout through the modify workout option (when it is delivering random workouts to individuals). We should backfill every workout to be set as Both for now. This will apply to Normal Workouts, Shred, and Cardio.xtends '@KnpMenu/menu.html.twig' %}

{% block label %}
    {% if item.extra('icon') is not null %}
        <i class="{{ item.extra('icon') }}"></i>
    {% endif %}
    {{ parent() }}
{% endblock %}

{% block item %}
    {% if item.displayed %}
        {% if matcher.isCurrent(item) %}
            {% do item.setLinkAttribute('class', item.getLinkAttribute('class') ~ ' ' ~ options.currentClass) %}
        {% endif %}
        {{ parent() }}
    {% endif %}
{% endblock %}